snippet.title: Britney Spears Calls Out Christina Aguilera For Avoiding Question
snippet.description:
Britney Spears isn't holding back. The pop superstar weighed in on a recent Christina Aguilera interview at the 2021 Latin Grammys, in which the singer was asked if she's been in touch with Britney. In the clip, Christina's team quickly shut the question down, with the pop star replying that she's happy for her fellow icon. The "Womanizer" songstress took issue with the situation and shared her thoughts about it on her Instagram story on Friday.
